{"tid":1487140,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔明捉鬼同起大台點解無分別嘅同我入嚟","createTime":"2019-08-19T06:39:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T08:37:58.000Z","uid":125902,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"4244a40379adb4c20c2374bfa06e2f1199b9099d","tid":1487140,"uid":125902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T06:39:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">#乜野係無大台</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">無大台＝去中央化、自發、多元：</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">去中央化</span><br />\n令到政治上可以be water，「領袖」唔會受到過大壓力，「群眾」都唔洗再驚被背叛，對家更加搵唔到對頭人做離間。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">自發</span><br />\n每個人唔會因為需要接收指令先做野，行動變得有效率，唔似啲冒警咁係條街企最少半個鐘再跑500米。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">多元</span><br />\n每個人擅長野唔一樣，自己會搵到自覺最適合嘅角色；更重要係，我地知道自己唔係樣樣叻，所以一定會有人做啲同自己唔同嘅野，百花齊放，互補不足，產生協同效應。<br />\n<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">#乜野叫大台</span></span><br />\n好多人會覺得「大台」等於由上而下司令台， 又或者係政客吸光舞台，其實：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大台就係「強逼」、「統一」、「共識」三為一體。</span><br />\n<br />\n例子一：「今日只係和理非」<br />\n1. #強逼 所有人只可以和理非<br />\n2. #統一 所有人只可以和理非<br />\n3. 覺得今日和理非係全世界 #共識<br />\n所以，「今日只係和理非」哩句就係大台。<br />\n<br />\n例子二：「光復香港，時代革命」<br />\n1. 無人強逼你認同／叫出口<br />\n2. 無人話過要綱領統一<br />\n（就算五大訴求都好，提出額外野都無人反對你）<br />\n3. 大家都好忙，你唔需要同人就哩句口號產生共識<br />\n所以，「光復香港，時代革命」就唔係大台。（如果覺得口號太兒戲，可以用五大訴求run多次，都唔係大台）<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n<br />\n所以，尋晚小部分「激進和非理」指出「<span style=\"color: red;\">邊個留低邊個係鬼呀</span>」，就係：<br />\n1+2. #強逼_統一 所有人離開現場；唔離開甚至就唔係自己人<br />\n3. 自覺行完就走係全世界共識<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">醒目嘅大家睇到哩到，你就知大台關鍵唔係共識，都唔係統一，而係強逼。<br />\n<br />\n和理非絕對唔係問題，但係大台就係問題，唔知自己係大台既大台就更加係問題中嘅問題。<br />\n<br />\n而同時，「激進和理非」更加視無大台當中嘅「多元」元素為無物、壓制埋「自發」元素，甚至走火入魔地產生不信任。<br />\n<br />\n簡單啲，咁樣嘅自我離間，就係大台思維走火入魔之極致。</span><br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">#點樣捉鬼好</span></span><br />\n其實全部無樣睇架，靠外貌同裝備去睇真係太低智啦，又花心神。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">總之：<br />\n1. 唔好做街頭版中計黨<br />\n唔好認定陣地戰、過激行為就係鬼；用下個腦，考慮當刻風險成效，現場自決。<br />\n2. 鬼永遠同01一樣：「關鍵時刻，體態盡現」<br />\n電光石火，有人阻你，想捉你落地，仲要冒埋警，你唔搞死佢你已經好厚道。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n等我學政府先<br />\n<br />\n完"},{"pid":"4ef898b55a0dce1e4e6aa63cdc1bec7869e15e16","tid":1487140,"uid":125902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T06:39:38.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3921b46fee6a85d4b07d32645fc73ecdcf66c284","tid":1487140,"uid":125902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T06:39:53.000Z","msg":"自推第二下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e831f51f4c3190f8c6716d45a04a51429e48425f","tid":1487140,"uid":125902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T06:40:12.000Z","msg":"自推三下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00cbd27404403e1603a30700acbb5afe39412344","tid":1487140,"uid":125902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T06:40:29.000Z","msg":"快啲推比啲唔明嘅人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"626d8fd249e8ba8e792271819c3efc76c20c15cc","tid":1487140,"uid":152241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T06:41:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e537d8dd5a31658353ac70dcb0b623e454508b6d","tid":1487140,"uid":95425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T06:42:05.000Z","msg":"睇唔明推住先"},{"pid":"a7a03078abca4db0f460f0d73a179906370e3ecb","tid":1487140,"uid":103569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T06:42:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"25e3aeb0a18ae0e4774313cd945cbda336eb524b","tid":1487140,"uid":282490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T06:43:38.000Z","msg":"中共維穩：今星期開始吹緊咩風, 打緊咩主意?<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dGEbNS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dGEbNS</a>"},{"pid":"c53de8dd31eabf812ebe7eb585f9ef752d73bc32","tid":1487140,"uid":153797,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T06:43:54.000Z","msg":"一句到尾， 去之前set個target比自己<br />\n做完就離開， 唔好太理現場指示， 唔好聽人哋講共識<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要走嘅，安全咁走， <br />\n要留嘅， 搵個信得過嘅人組成小隊"},{"pid":"0654dcb9feaa9e62d679be2b89f2bf4531106835","tid":1487140,"uid":44461,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T06:50:56.000Z","msg":"推 講得好好<br />\n<br />\n建立大台而不知自己是大台"},{"pid":"111ba34a6124bb8b6279ea407d02e55e26bcadae","tid":1487140,"uid":273450,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T06:53:11.000Z","msg":"手動正評<br />\n<br />\n總之唔好掛住捉鬼啦!"},{"pid":"89f8b1989b718e16f69d9a75d89ef2be78edeca2","tid":1487140,"uid":125902,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T07:01:27.000Z","msg":"不要大台啊！！"},{"pid":"0171160d2a645283a143a46e2371c88144275efc","tid":1487140,"uid":125902,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T07:01:42.000Z","msg":"唔好再捉鬼喇！！"},{"pid":"0f7c6b97692cb31b6ceb7e1bf3c5241e8d9c7ce8","tid":1487140,"uid":103569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T07:25:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9366ee3980cbe43090d3d63093d22356062961e5","tid":1487140,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T07:27:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33d520a87dd23a60159cd2918f3d4c3ad5f0b7f6","tid":1487140,"uid":152241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T07:28:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4817b128b1dccbdff5da8a489690747ef6ce7cd8","tid":1487140,"uid":148709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T07:40:06.000Z","msg":"